Darkwind help for screenreader users.

This help path is shown first because your screenreader setting is on. If a
screenreader-specific help topic exists, you will hear that version. If it does
not exist yet, Darkwind falls back to the normal help topic.

New to Darkwind? Type help guide for a short, stage-by-stage walkthrough
from your first steps to the endgame.

Good first commands:

help basics look
  How to read your current room.

help basics exits
  How to find where you can move.

help basics npcs
  How to list non-player characters in the room.

help basics players
  How to list other players in the room.

help basics items
  How to list visible items in the room.

help basics actions
  How to find room-specific actions, things to look at, and things to read.

help basics inventory
  How to review what you are carrying.

help interface screenreader
  How to turn screenreader support on or off.

Useful commands while exploring:

look
exits
npcs
players
items
actions
inventory
score
who

Use help list to hear the available help sections. Use help list basics to hear
topics in the basics section.
